outcome.population:
Three participants had to be excluded from this analysis:
mid-therapy PET images got lost due to a technical error;
pre-therapy scanning procedure had 40 seconds delayed start, preventing the modeling of parametric outcomes;
pathologic response could not be evaluated due to a metastatic disease progression prior to surgery.

